    %h1.hdg-s Marketing Automation
    %h2 How marketing automation can make your life easier by saving time and money.
    = image_tag( 'marketing-automation-resources.jpg', alt: 'marketing automation', class: 'pull-right img-polaroid', title: 'Marketing Automation' )
    %p 
      Marketing automation describes the use of software or the functionality of a marketing platform to help a business automate specific marketing processes.  The advantage is that time and resources no longer have to be spent on routine or repetitive functions.  In addition to saving time, marketing automation can be useful in helping to identify industry best practices or recommending the best of different alternatives.
    %p
      For example, many marketing automation programs help manage the sales funnel - from identifying a lead to negotiating with a prospect to onboarding a customer.
    %p
      In evaluating marketing platforms, make sure you consider the extent and level of marketing automation that is built in.
    %p
      %strong
        Here are just a few of the automated features of Optyn’s marketing platform.
      %ul.bullet-disc
        %li 
          %strong Syndication.
          Marketing campaigns and promotions are syndicated across email, social media and other channels.
        %li 
          %strong Subject Line Suggestions.
          Subject lines that generate the highest open rates are pre-filled into the subject field.
        %li 
          %strong Form Fields.
          Pick the type of campaign you want to run and Optyn presents you with the appropriate data fields to complete.
        %li 
          %strong Mobile Responsive.
          You don’t have to worry how your email will look on different devices. Optyn has made sure that the email will be perfect whether it is opened on a laptop, tablet or smartphone.
    %p
      As you evaluate other programs, make sure as many processes are automated as possible. You’ll be glad you did.
